{"tid":952811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［失蹤人口］網民認不出徐子珊","createTime":"2018-12-23T12:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-30T13:25:17.000Z","uid":215823,"like":25,"dislike":448,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"3546a914ec7a1f035d41b7a69503f194e02d071f","tid":952811,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"闊別香港觀眾一段時間的徐子珊，先後參加了「愛奇藝」的真人騷節目《吃光全宇宙》，之後在今年6月飛到北京拍攝一齣時裝劇，而且要逗留整整一個月，在內地拍劇擁有的優厚待遇，當然跟香港電視台一天一地，但長期留在內地發展，少了曝光率，本地觀眾又出名善忘，還會有幾多人記得子珊可謂未知之數。不過醒目的子珊，亦不時在微博更新自己近況，同時付上近照，讓粉絲可以有機會上網見見子珊。<br />\n<br />\n不過近月子珊上載微博的相片，網民即紛紛留言表示「係咪貼錯圖？」、「大陸feel」、「以前正好多」，究竟是否P圖得過份，還是有其他原因？莫非逗留在內地太耐，連氣質都有逆天的變化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/23/203859_63882cd71b721522e3598edf7f9f7a79.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F203859_63882cd71b721522e3598edf7f9f7a79.png&h=6bd22589&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/23/203900_4dddf40080f8ed6ff595b4770a6b75c7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F203900_4dddf40080f8ed6ff595b4770a6b75c7.png&h=855837fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/23/203902_701d25a4a4f0c477012e924bc561c0f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F203902_701d25a4a4f0c477012e924bc561c0f0.png&h=f5653349&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3ea777599ab2c95927f0ac051587846328ffb75","tid":952811,"uid":27605,"like":103,"dislike":9,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"黑絲"},{"pid":"2f3b976689891a5400fdd217eea37d5efce11a01","tid":952811,"uid":38904,"like":490,"dislike":4,"score":486,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"整容失敗？"},{"pid":"7bfe88b9dd55077c60e34e0687fdcef2b3ce8f59","tid":952811,"uid":828,"like":183,"dislike":5,"score":178,"citedBy":2,"replyTim